## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of historical data and the potential biases in historical records. Additionally, the motivations for immigration are complex and multifaceted, and this report may not capture all individual experiences or lesser-known factors influencing immigration. The focus was primarily on historical trends, which may not fully represent contemporary immigration dynamics.